		Fundaci&oacute;n Paniamor, Costa Rica<BR>
		Grupo de Apoyo Nacional a la Convenci&oacute;n de los<BR>
		derechos del ni&ntilde;o, Chile<BR>
		Integra&ccedil;&acirc;o da Marginaldo, Brasil<BR>
		Centre for the Prevention and Treatment of Abuse, Filipinas<BR>
		Good Shepherd Sisters, Taiwan<BR>
		Kalungan sa Erma, Filipinas<BR>
		Domestic Workers Movement, India<BR>
