<P><H2>World Congress Against Commercial Sexual Exploitation of Children</H2></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT>
<P><IMG src="122_1.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE>

<P><H2>Press contact</H2><BR>
A joint press bureau for UNICEF, ECPAT and the NGO Group on the Rights of the Child is operated out of the UNICEF office in Geneva.  Please contact: June Kane, Media Advisor, World Congress, c/o UNICEF Information Geneva, Palais des Nations, 1211 Geneva 10, Swtizerland.  E-mail: jkane@unicef.ch.
