<body background="../images/paper.jpg" text="#0000A0">
<h1>Competition and Litigation Support</h1>
<hr>
<h2>Services provided</h2>
<p>Ever since its formation in 1986, LE has provided clients with
expert assistance in cases involving UK and EC competition law,
contractual and trade disputes, and many other areas of
commercial law. Our expertise covers:</p>
<ul>
    <li>competition authority investigation support</li>
    <li>merger submissions</li>
    <li>litigation support</li>
    <li>advice on industry regulation</li>
    <li>damage measurement</li>
    <li>valuation of intellectual property</li>
</ul>
<p>Acting alongside lawyers, or directly with clients, our highly
experienced team quickly identifies the key issues on which cases
are decided. We formulate appropriate strategies, prepare
submissions or expert witness statements, and attend hearings and
give evidence. </p>
<h3>Key benefits</h3>
<p>As specialist economic consultants, we provide a different
service to that offered by the large accounting firms on the one
hand, and independent consulting academic economists on the
other. Working to strict deadlines, we develop arguments based on
state of the art economic analysis. Where appropriate, these are
strengthened by detailed market research, sophisticated
simulation techniques or econometric models. Our evidence is
concise and compelling.</p>
