<h4>This is a complete list of articles from London Economics'
newsletter &quot;<i>Economics in Action</i>&quot; and our <i>&quot;Competition
and Regulation Bulletin&quot;</i>. These articles have been
written by LE's team of expert economists and deal with many of
the most important issues in micro- and macro-economic policy,
both in the UK and overseas. Click on the topic you are
interested in to see summaries of the articles. Then. if you want
to read the full article, click on the title of the piece. </h4>
<hr>
<p><font size="5"><cite><strong>Economics in Action</strong></cite></font></p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="../pubs/newslet/1996_4.htm"><font size="4">Issue
        4 1996 </font></a></li>
    <li><a href="../pubs/newslet/1996_3.htm"><font size="4">Issue
        3 1996</font></a></li>
    <li><a href="../pubs/newslet/1996_2.htm"><font size="4">Issue
        2 1996 </font></a></li>
    <li><a href="../pubs/newslet/1996_1.htm"><font size="4">Issue
        1 1996</font></a><font size="4"> </font></li>
</ul>
