http://www.londecon.co.uk:80/pubs/newslet/whatsina.htm 194.193.150.111 19970111012930 text/html 8402
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:24:16 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
