<DOCOLDNO>IA036-000712-B014-66</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.londecon.co.uk:80/pubs/internat/markets.htm 194.193.150.111 19970111013734 text/html 3726
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:32:28 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 3555
Last-modified: Sat, 14 Sep 1996 15:05:31 GMT
