<DOCNO>WT11-B06-109</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA036-000712-B018-242</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.londecon.co.uk:80/pubs/media/oscars.htm 194.193.150.111 19970111015053 text/html 4070
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:45:46 GMT
