http://www.londecon.co.uk:80/pubs/privat/infrajam.htm 194.193.150.111 19970111015950 text/html 6769
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 01:54:43 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
