<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Unicorn News</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#FF0080" ALINK="#008000"></BODY>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="uninews.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<P><B>On this page you will find information about Unicorn Internet and the
Internet.</B></P></CENTER>
<P><I>Last updated 5/11/96<IMG SRC="play.gif" border=2 ALIGN="left"></P></I>
<P>Unicorn Internet plans <b>ISDN</b> connection. Installation of ISDN will 
go ahead and should be available to Unicorn clients before the end of 
December '96. More information will be given on this page in the coming weeks.</P>
<P>There will be a <b>FULL</b> upgrade to Unicorn Internet. More callin 
lines, a new high speed router/modem connection and an upgrade to the 
lease-line. Completion should be before the end of December '96. More information will be given in the coming weeks on this page.</P> 
<P>If you have any interesting information for other users please e-mail to<A HREF="mailto:bob@mcs.nl">Bob Martin.</A> I will then include
 your news on this page, (such as events, interesting sites found on the 
Internet and so on).
<br>
<b>The ACCOUNT COSTS (ABONNEMENT OP UNICORN INTERNET). <a href="http://mcs.nl/cost.html">*Kosten.*</a></b>
<br>
<P>Local telephone area is 0320, 0321, 0341, 036.
<br>
<P>To access a Newsgroup Server, link to news.cybercomm.nl</B></P>
<hr>
<P>For <b>ALL</b> Internet Software and much more go to <a href="http://tucows.wau.nl/">Tucows.</a>
It has everything you will every need such as e-mail, browsers, ftp and WWW programs.....the list is endless!!
The following information was provided by <a href="mailto:marcel@mcs.nl">Marcel</a>. 
A fun site for users who like to e-mail! Take a look at <a href="http://www.adpost.nl/"> Posting of Postcards!</a></p>

<P>Unicorn Internet has activated its own FTP site, to access it use your FTP 
program and enter the DNS number (194.178.19.5).</P>

<H2>

<A HREF="http://mcs.nl/index2.html">Unicorn Internet</A></H2>
